Package: esaps
Type: Package
Title: Indicators of Electoral Systems and Party Systems
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Nicolas", 
                    family = "Schmidt", 
                    role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                    email = "nschmidt@cienciassociales.edu.uy",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5083-5792")))       
Description: It allows structuring electoral data of different size and structure 
        to calculate various indicators frequently used in the studies of electoral systems and party systems.
        Indicators of electoral volatility, electoral disproportionality, party nationalization and the 
        effective number of parties are included.
License: GPL-2
